- content_for :title do
	homepage
- content_for :bodyClass do
	homepage
%div
	%h1.section Welcome to AusNet Services
	.line
	%h3.section You can use this tool to get approval for an inverter energy system, e.g. solar panels, battery, up to 30kW capacity and 15kW export.
	.section
		For systems greater than 30kW, you need to apply for
		%a{:href=>"/request-assessment"} technical assessment.

	%h4 There are a few things you'll need before you use this tool:
	.section
		%div.checkbox
			%input{:type=>"checkbox", :id=>"monthly", :name=>"payment-freq", :value=>"monthly", :checked=>"checked"}
			%label{:for=>"monthly"} What sort of installation it is, eg solar / battery / wind
		%div.checkbox
			%input{:type=>"checkbox",:id=>"fortnightly", :name=>"payment-freq", :value=>"fortnightly"}
			%label{:for=>"fortnightly"} A copy of a recent electricity bill for the property (to get the NMI and meter number)
		%div.checkbox
			%input{:type=>"checkbox", :id=>"weekly", :name=>"payment-freq", :value=>"weekly"}
			%label{:for=>"weekly"} Details of the proposed inverters i.e. manufacturer and model
		%div.checkbox
			%input{:type=>"checkbox", :id=>"weekly", :name=>"payment-freq", :value=>"weekly"}
			%label{:for=>"weekly"} The expected total capacity and export requirements of the system
		%div.checkbox
			%input{:type=>"checkbox", :id=>"weekly", :name=>"payment-freq", :value=>"weekly"}
			%label{:for=>"weekly"} How many phases at the property (most are single phase)

%a.button{:href=>"/terms-conditions"}
	I've got all these things
%a.button.secondary{:href=>"/request-assessment"}
	I need a bigger installation
